title: Art Institute of Chicago Sweatshirt
description:
Sweatshirt developed from The Art Institute of Chicago logo designed by Abbot Miller, partner of Pentagram, 2009.

Though stacked vertically, the words “Art,” “Institute,” and “Chicago” each have equal weight, reflecting our continued commitment to our collection, our mission as an educational institution, and our deep connection to our city and our community.

  • Size: S, M, L, XL
  • Materials: 80% cotton, 20% polyester
  • Care Instructions included.
